snippet.title: Proper Printing
snippet.description: Proper Printing is all about 3D printing. My goal is to learn as much as possible about this awesome hobby and share these experiences with you. I'm exploring new things and try things out that haven't been done before and I don't know from the start if a new idea will be successful or not. What I do know is that I learn from these experiences and have a lot of fun doing it. Hopefully you do as well and that this might help you with your projects!
